data.description: Absolutely stunning one and a half story located on a corner lot in the sought after Woodtrace gated community. For added security, Woodtrace offers a manned guard shack from 8 pm to 6 am nightly. This four bedroom and three full bath beautiful and barely lived-in home will surely not disappoint! Large living area w/ corner fireplace. Large secondary bedrooms w/ high ceilings!  Upstairs guest suite plus an oversized game room or media area. Open kitchen with tons of cabinets and countertop space over looking the large family room. Oversized master with a huge master bath is just perfect!  This floor plan offers so much versatility for the discerning buyer. With its spacious layout, luxurious features, and prime corner lot location, this home is truly a gem Don't miss the opportunity to make it your own and enjoy the Pinehurst lifestyle in a home that truly has it all. Come experience the epitome of Southern charm in Woodtrace and luxury living. Tomball Schools. Close to everything.
